Package GoNature

Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.Employee
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Employee represents an employee working within the system. Each employee has a unique ID and various details such as first name, last name, worker ID, email, role, username, password, park ID, and authority level. This class provides methods to get and set employee details.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim, Nadine Halabi
    See Also:
